Le '''Indo-Evropikane chiba''' si yek chibavipnaski familiya, anderyarindoy le buteder [[chib]]a andar i [[Evropa]], but andar i [[Sudutni Asiya]], [[Sudovestutni Asiya]] tay [[Mashkarutni Asiya]]. La si la o buteder gin le vakyarnengo mashkar sa le familiyande. Le [[Indo-Irane chiba]] si i bareder Indo-Evropikani rig.
[[Chitro:IndoEuropeanTree.svg|thumb|300px|Indo-Evropikane chiba]]

== Xulavipen ==
Le riga le Indo-Evropikane chibange si (rendyarde palal lengo puranipen):
* [[Anatolikane chiba]], i puraneder jangli rig, katar o [[18to shelbersh aX]], akana muli (xasardi), anderyarindoy i chib le [[hititurya|hititurengo]]
* [[Indo-Irane chiba]], biyandile andar i [[Anglal Indo Irani chib]]
** [[Indo-Ariyane chiba]], anderyarindoy i [[Sanskrtikani]], jangle andar o mashkar le duyto miebershengo
** [[Irane chiba]], jangle andar opretele [[1000 aX]] sar i [[Avestani]], tay andar [[520 aX]] i [[Purani Persikani]]
** [[Dardikane chhiba]]
** [[Nuristane chhiba]]
* [[Yelenikani (Grekikani) chib]], i puraneder jangli si i [[Micheneyani chhib]] ([[14to shelbersh aX]])
* [[Italikane chiba]], anderyarindoi i [[Latinikani chib|Latinikani]] tay laki visa, le [[Romanikane chiba]] ([[7to shelbersh aX]])
* [[Seltikane chiba]], Gelikane lekhipena andar o [[6to shelbersh aX]]
* [[Jermanikani chib]], le puraneder lekhipena andar o [[2to shelbersh aX]]
* [[Armenikani chib]], andar o [[5to shelbersh]]
* [[Toxariyane chiba]], i muli chib le [[Toxara|Toxarengo]], andar o [[6to shelbersh]]
* [[Balto-Slavikane chhiba]], varesave manusha phenen ke sas yek Purani Balto-Slavikani chib, aver phenen ke nas kadya.
** [[Slavikane chiba]], andar o [[9to shelbersh]], le puraneder lekha pi [[Purani Khangeryaki Slavikani]]
** [[Baltikane chiba]], andar o [[14to shelbersh]]
* [[Shkipikani chib]] (Albanikani), andar o [[15to shelbersh]].

Avryal le kadale desh riga, sas varesave chiba, mule vay sira jangle:

* [[Iliriyane chiba]]
* [[Venetikane chib]] pashal le Italikane
* [[Liburniyani chib]] 
* [[Mesapiyani chib]] nai jangli mishto
* [[Frijiyani chib]], purani chib andar i [[Frijiya]], fal te avel pashal i Yelinikani, Trachikani vay Armenikani
* [[Payonyani chhib]], muli chib ko nordo la [[Makedoniya]]ko
* [[Trachikani chib]], fal te avel pashal i Dachikani
* [[Dachikani chhib]], fal te avel pashal i Trachikani
* [[Purani Makedonikani chib]], fal te avel pashal i Yelinikani, aver phenen ke sas pashal i Ilirikani, Trachikani vai Frijiyani
* [[Ligurikani chib]], chi janel pes kana sas chachi Indo-Evropikani, fal te avel pashal i Seltikani

Si dudalo ke sas aver chiba akana mule bi te janas vareso pe lende. Nay dudalo kana i [[Retikani chib]] sas Indo-Evropikani.
=== Satem tay Sentum chiba ===
But godyaver manusha xulaven le Indo-Evropikane chiba pe chiba Satem vay Sentum.

